description: Expansion of theta_3(q) * theta_3(q^12) + theta_2(q) * theta_2(q^12) in powers of q^(1/4).
mathematica: a[ n_] := SeriesCoefficient[ EllipticTheta[ 3, 0, x] EllipticTheta[ 3, 0, x^12] + EllipticTheta[ 2, 0, x] EllipticTheta[ 2, 0, x^12], {x, 0, n/4}]; (* _Michael Somos_, Feb 22 2015 *)
prog: (PARI) {a(n) = my(A); if( n<0, 0, A = x * O(x^n); polcoeff( (eta(x^8 + A) * eta(x^96+A))^5 / (eta(x^4 + A) * eta(x^16 + A) * eta(x^48 + A) * eta(x^192 + A))^2 + 4*x^13 * (eta(x^16 + A) * eta(x^192 + A))^2 / (eta(x^8 + A) * eta(x^96 + A)), n))};
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_.
